HEADWORD: Clubfoot
<hw>Club"foot</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Club</ets> +
<ets>foot</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A short, variously
distorted foot; also, the deformity, usually congenital, which such a
foot exhibits; talipes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Clubfooted</ent>⟦br⟧
